Thomson-East Coast Line (TEL) MRT Guide – Stations and Nearby Condos

The Thomson-East Coast Line (TEL) is the newest MRT line to begin operation, with the first stations having opened in January 2020. Here is how the future MRT network map will look when the entire TEL is operational.

TEL stages and opening dates -

Stage 1 (already operational): Woodlands North, Woodlands and Woodlands South

Stage 2 (already operational): Springleaf, Lentor, Mayflower, Bright Hill, Upper Thomson and Caldecott

Stage 3 (already operational): Mount Pleasant, Stevens, Napier, Orchard Boulevard, Orchard, Great World, Havelock, Outram Park, Maxwell, Shenton Way, Marina Bay, Marina South and Gardens by the Bay

Stage 4 (2024): Founders' Memorial, Tanjong Rhu, Katong Park, Tanjong Katong, Marine Parade, Marine Terrace, Siglap and Bayshore

Stage 5 (2025): Bedok South and Sungei Bedok
